markets.title: Will the Nasdaq-100 be above 18043.85 at the end of Mar 1, 2024?
markets.rules_primary: If the Nasdaq 100 index close value for March 01, 2024 is above 18043.85, then the market resolves to Yes.
markets.rules_secondary:
The market will close at 4:00 PM ET on March 01, 2024. The market will expire at the sooner of the first 7:00 PM ET after the release of the data, or one week after March 01, 2024.

Pursuant to the Kalshi Rulebook, the Exchange has modified the Source Agency and Underlying for indices markets. See the rules for more information.
